               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260216-51-person502">
                  WALTER 
                  THORNHILL
               <interp inst="t18260216-51-person502" type="surname" value="THORNHILL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260216-51-person502" type="given" value="WALTER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260216-51-person502" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I know the dozen scissors to be part of those which I put in the package; I knew them by the kind of scissor - we had not a dozen of this pattern, and put in two others to make up; I know all these parcels, and this No. 28, I can identify in particular.</p>
